            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "警破旺角快富街淫窟檢避孕套毛巾 57歲男主持被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b889c31e7cee2da01315beea3f2645d9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040322411854468.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>旺角警區特別職務隊人員根據線報及經深入調查後今日（3日）下午展開代號「搜鷁」的掃黃行動，突擊搜查快富街一單位，搗破一個懷疑賣淫場所。<br/>\n<br/>\n人員於單位內以涉嫌「管理賣淫場所」拘捕一名57歲男子。人員亦檢獲記帳簿、避孕套、毛巾等證物。該名被捕人已被控一項「管理賣淫場所」罪，案件將於5月7日在西九龍裁判法院提堂。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176000/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方檢獲記帳簿、避孕套、毛巾等證物。警方提供\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ffd65ce2980c7251f07818f42d07efb3/2025-04/STEMPICKER__SDS_2_MKDIST_2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方檢獲記帳簿、避孕套、毛巾等證物。警方提供\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176001/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方以涉嫌「管理賣淫場所」拘捕一名57歲男子。警方提供\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d912ebd453b7f53dc5f1913f6d2af66a/2025-04/STEMPICKER__SDS_2_MKDIST_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方以涉嫌「管理賣淫場所」拘捕一名57歲男子。警方提供\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
